summaries.full: Season Four Finale. In a final attempt to save Pied Piper from ruin, Richard finds himself caught up in a web of lies. Concerned about Richard's future, Jared plans his exit; Jack bets big in an attempt to change the narrative. Gavin plots his comeback.

summaries.short: Season Five Premiere. Richard faces new challenges as a leader as Pied Piper levels up; Gavin worries about being antiquated.
summaries.full: Season Five Premiere. Now that Pied Piper has ample funding and new offices, the pressure to get things right stymies Richard and forces him to grow the company in a way he hadn't planned. A picky Dinesh and Gilfoyle question their ability to make good decisions. After returning to Hooli, Gavin worries about the prospect of becoming antiquated.
